lead_paragraph: Defending champion Agnieszka Radwanska took the final spot in the semifinals of the WTA Finals, beating Karolina Pliskova 7-5, 6-3 on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Radwanska Advances to Semifinals at WTA Finals
